  },
  {
    question: "Can you accommodate young professionals with busy schedules?",
    answer: "Absolutely. Mountain Brook Village attracts successful young professionals and dual-income couples who work demanding jobs. We clean while you're at the office, provide key or smart lock access, and lock up securely when finished. Many clients schedule bi-weekly or weekly service so they can actually enjoy their evenings and weekends instead of cleaning."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you clean renovated historic homes and cottages?",
    answer: "Yes! The Village has many beautifully renovated properties - updated 1930s-1950s homes with modern kitchens, renovated baths, and preserved character details. We understand how to care for both the historic charm (original hardwoods, vintage tile, built-ins) and modern finishes (quartz counters, new appliances, contemporary fixtures). Best of both worlds requires specialized knowledge."
  },
  {
    question: "How do you handle homes close to the Village shopping area?",
    answer: "Many Village homes are within walking distance of shops and restaurants - that's the appeal! We're experienced with tighter parking situations, coordinate arrival times to avoid disruption, and maintain quiet, professional operations that respect your neighbors. We understand urban-adjacent living requires consideration."
  },
  {
    question: "What's included in regular maintenance for Village homes?",
    answer: "Our regular service (weekly or bi-weekly) covers all living areas, bedrooms, bathrooms, kitchen, dusting, vacuuming, mopping, and general tidying. We focus on keeping your home company-ready for the entertaining lifestyle the Village encourages. Same team every visit means consistency and efficiency - they know your preferences and your home's quirks."
  },
  {
    question: "Can you help with pre-party cleaning and post-event cleanup?",
    answer: "Definitely! Village residents love to entertain - dinner parties, book clubs, holiday gatherings. We provide pre-event deep cleaning to ensure your home sparkles, and post-event cleanup to restore order. Living in the Village means spontaneous entertaining - we help make it effortless rather than stressful."
